The UN has proposed a plan in Cancun yesterday to renew the lighting of households, trade and industry in 100 countries in order to achieve a reduction in greenhouse gas (GHG) that corresponds to almost a third of the additional reduction that must be realized to stabilize the Earth’s climate by 2020.
